    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Wait, you're saying the slippery slope is just fearmongering? That's a pretty strong stance. I was asking for philosophical arguments to help my blog post, but it feels like you're completely dismissing the perspective I'm trying to explore. Can you actually provide the philosophical counter-arguments to the safety premise instead of just calling them scare tactics?",
